  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject bearing of one to five intellectual metastases of lung origin at the time of
             the indication of the radiosurgery

          -  Subject requiring a radiosurgical treatment with LGK

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject having hurts of the brainstem or para-optics

          -  Pregnant women or in feeding period

          -  Subject having received previously a split conventional radiotherapy
      </textblock>
